Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.09,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:408971,410097}I guess I'll join you.{NOTE:そうね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:07:00.06,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:417480,420066}Oh? The practice's over already?{NOTE:—あら？\\N—練習終わったのかしら？}
