Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:07.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:426447,427531}Naka, what about training?{NOTE:ナカ 練習は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.28,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:429283,431285}Well, Professor Shimizu…{NOTE:それが清水先生が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:12.91,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:431285,432912}Huh? Professor Shimizu what?{NOTE:えっ？ 清水先生が？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.41,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:432912,434413}Professor Shimizu!{NOTE:清水先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:18.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:437416,438584}Professor Shimizu…{NOTE:清水先生…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:26.34,Alternative,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:443089,446342}I shouldn't have agreed\Nto that three-player match after all.{NOTE:やはり３人バレーなんて やるべきではなかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.88,Alternative,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:446342,447885}It was too much of a shock to them.{NOTE:ショックが大きすぎたわ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:34.55,Alternative,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:449762,454558}I don't have what it takes\Nto support them.{NOTE:私には これ以上 彼女たちを 引っ張っていく力がない}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.47,Alternative,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:454558,456477}There's only one way left.{NOTE:残された方法は ただ１つ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.98,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:459939,461983}I'm sorry, Professor Shimizu.{NOTE:残念ですが清水先生}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.77,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:461983,463776}I'm afraid I can't help you.{NOTE:コーチ就任は お断りします}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:50.40,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:463776,470408}We have many outstanding players such as\NAyuhara-san, yet I don't know what to do at all.{NOTE:鮎原さんをはじめ すばらしい選手が そろってるって いうのに 私の力では どうすることも できないんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.57,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:472702,475579}I'm a novice at coaching.{NOTE:コーチとして 素人の私に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:58.12,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:475579,478124}I understand your\Nsituation all too well.{NOTE:ええ 事情は 私にも よく分かります}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:03.58,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:480501,483587}But I still have to refuse.{NOTE:しかし やはり お断りする以外にない}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.29,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:483587,486298}Professor Hongou…{NOTE:本郷先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:09.76,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:486298,489760}I'm busy, Professor Shimizu.\NExcuse me, please.{NOTE:清水先生 忙しいので これで失礼します}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.27,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:504066,506277}Everyone's so depressed.{NOTE:みんなが 意気消沈している}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:29.19,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:506277,509196}None of us can prepare for a game\Nthat we've already lost anyway.{NOTE:でも望みのない戦いに ファイトは湧かないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:31.74,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:509196,511741}No matter how much\Nwe love volleyball…{NOTE:たとえ どんなに バレーを愛していても}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.99,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:512908,514994}Stop it, everyone!{NOTE:—みんな やめて\\N—えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:35.87,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:514994,515870}Oonuma-san!{NOTE:大沼さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:38.78,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:515870,518789}Why can't you just give\Npractice your all?{NOTE:みんな なぜ こんなに だらけた練習しか できないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:43.21,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:518789,523210}If you really like volleyball, if you love it,\Nsnap out of it already!{NOTE:ほんとに バレーが好きなら バレーを 愛してるなら いいかげんに ショックから 立ち直るべきだわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:46.96,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:523210,526964}And yet here you are, getting depressed\Nover nothing. You're better off quitting.{NOTE:それなのに みんな勝手に ファイトをなくして しまうなんて やめた方がいいわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:51.17,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:526964,531177}Even if we can't win the Interhigh,\Nwe have to do our best!{NOTE:たとえインターハイで 優勝はできなくても みんなで 力いっぱい頑張るのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.08,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:561832,563084}Ayuhara!{NOTE:鮎原！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.04,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:563084,564043}Yes!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:26.75,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:565795,566754}Next!{NOTE:次！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:27.37,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:566754,567379}Yes!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:39.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:578682,579975}Midori!{NOTE:みどり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:42.77,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:579975,582770}Stand up, Hayakawa! Stand up!{NOTE:さあ 立つのよ 早川 立って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.43,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:582770,584438}What's with you?{NOTE:どうしたのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.43,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:584438,585439}I've had it!{NOTE:もうたくさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:585439,587399}Midori…{NOTE:みどり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:49.69,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:587399,589693}I'm fed with this nonsense practice!{NOTE:こんな うそっぱちの 練習なんて嫌よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:50.86,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:589693,590861}What did you just say?!{NOTE:何ですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:55.53,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:590861,595533}I don't see the point in practicing when\Nwe know that we're going to lose anyway!{NOTE:負ける… そう分かっていて なれ合いの練習だなんて 嫌よ 絶対に！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.78,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:595533,597785}– Huh?\N– Huh?{NOTE:ええ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:00.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:597785,600079}Midori, what are you saying?{NOTE:みどり 何てことを}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.16,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:600079,601163}Just what you heard.{NOTE:嫌なのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:05.54,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:601163,605543}This training is completely pointless\Nand you know it! Just stop pretending!{NOTE:誰のためとか何とか言って みんなは 結局 自分をごまかしてるんだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.87,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:605543,607878}I'm not going to keep up\Nwith this charade anymore!{NOTE:そんな練習なんて たくさんだって 言ってるのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.21,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:611132,613217}Professor!{NOTE:先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:20.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:619390,620808}Captain…{NOTE:キャプテン}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:33.40,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:631944,633404}P-Professor Hongou!{NOTE:ほ… 本郷先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:36.61,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:635072,636615}Professor!{NOTE:先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:41.95,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:639285,641954}You girls!\NWhy are you sitting on the court?!{NOTE:お前たち このざまは 一体 何だ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.45,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:641954,644456}We're going to fix this team\Nright away! Line up!{NOTE:俺がたたき直してやるから １列に並べ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:50.17,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:647626,650171}This kind of practice\Ngets us nowhere.{NOTE:こんな練習では どうにもならん}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:53.92,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:650171,653924}I'll arrange a training camp\Nat a university for you.{NOTE:全員を大学の寮に合宿させる 分かったな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:653924,655426}Professor Hongou!{NOTE:本郷先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.24,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:677573,679241}What's wrong, Kozue?{NOTE:どうしたの？ こずえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.20,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:683454,685206}You still want to practice?{NOTE:まだ練習？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.95,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:685206,686957}I just thought of something.{NOTE:今 急に思いついたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:29.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:686957,689710}I feel like I realized\Na weak point in my spike.{NOTE:私のスパイクの欠点が 分かったような気がして}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.09,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:694048,696091}Ah, it's no use…{NOTE:ああ… 駄目だわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:41.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:698177,701430}There's a big difference between\Nthinking of something and doing it.{NOTE:やっぱり 頭の中と やってみるのでは 大違いね}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.72,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:701430,704725}A weak point?\NDid Professor Hongou point something out?{NOTE:欠点だなんて 本郷先生がそう言ったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:47.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:704725,707269}No. It's just my intuition.{NOTE:ううん ただ 何となく}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:50.39,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:707269,710397}You're thinking too much.\NYou're too young to develop a neurosis.{NOTE:考え過ぎよ ノイローゼになる年でもないでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:53.23,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:710397,713234}Go to bed already.\NCome on, Kozue.{NOTE:さあ 早く寝ましょうよ ねっ こずえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:713234,714318}Yeah…{NOTE:ええ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:17.46,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:735005,737466}Kozue, you're still up?{NOTE:こずえ 寝ないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:19.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:737466,739260}Just a second.{NOTE:うん 今}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:27.72,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:746642,747726}That's it, Forehead.{NOTE:あれよ デコ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:30.43,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:747726,750437}That's the Fujimi High's trademark,\Nthe machine gun attack.{NOTE:あれが富士見高 18番 マシンガンアタック}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:32.43,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:750437,752439}Hmm. Machine gun attack, huh?{NOTE:うーん マシンガンアタックか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.19,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:753357,755192}It certainly is a unique technique.{NOTE:確かに貴重な得点源だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:38.11,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:756360,758112}But it won't be of much use.{NOTE:しかし 役には立たん}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:40.82,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:759280,760823}But why, Professor?!{NOTE:なぜですか？ 先生}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:43.90,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:760823,763909}We learned it specifically\Nto use against the Yagisawa sisters.{NOTE:八木沢三姉妹にだって通用したのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:45.20,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:763909,765202}Oh, you did.{NOTE:通用した}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.62,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:765202,766620}But it's only worked once so far.{NOTE:たった一度きりな}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:47.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:766620,767579}Huh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.83,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:767579,769832}Fine, I'll explain it thoroughly.{NOTE:この際 みんなも聞いておけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:53.62,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:769832,773627}The opponent we'll meet at the Interhigh\Nare nothing like the ones we played with so far.{NOTE:インターハイでぶつかる相手は 今までの相手とは桁違いだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:58.59,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:773627,778590}A technique that worked once\Nwon't work second time against them.{NOTE:一度 通用した戦法が 二度も役に立つと思ったら とんだことになる}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.34,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:778590,780342}For example,\Nlet's take you, Ayuhara.{NOTE:例えば 鮎原}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.46,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:780342,781468}Sir.{NOTE:はい}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:04.84,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:781468,784847}You certainly were an excellent\Nattacker in middle school.{NOTE:君は確かに 中学時代 すばらしいアタッカーだった}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:09.85,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:784847,789852}However, it's dubious how far you can go\Nat the Interhigh. It's on whole another level.{NOTE:だが 一回りレベルの違う インターハイで 君がどこまでやれるか疑問だな}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:15.23,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:791645,795232}The game with the Yagisawa sisters\Nthe other day has proved that very well.{NOTE:それは 既に先日の 八木沢姉妹の試合で証明済みだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:18.11,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:795232,798110}Ayuhara's spike, no matter\Nhow you look at it, has no weak points.{NOTE:鮎原のスパイクに どこといって欠点はない}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:21.03,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:798110,801030}But it's just a textbook spike.{NOTE:ちんまりとまとまって 教科書どおりのスパイクだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:24.99,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:801030,804992}Because of that, a professional player\Nwill immediately see right through it.{NOTE:それだけに キャリアのある選手なら たちまち球筋を見破ってしまう}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:31.24,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:806327,811248}If Ayuhara-san's spike isn't enough,\Nwhat about the team?{NOTE:鮎原さんが 戦力にならないとしたら…チームはどうなんのよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:35.33,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:811248,815336}Forget Jidōin, we might\Nnot even be able to beat Misawa.{NOTE:寺堂院どころか美沢にだって 勝てやしないじゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:38.25,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:815753,818255}We can't rely solely on Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さんに頼ろうとした 私たちがいけないのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:43.17,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:819340,823177}All of us have shared responsibility\Non the match score.{NOTE:私たちの一人一人の動きが 全ての得点につながる}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:45.34,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:823177,825346}Offense is said\Nto be the greatest defense.{NOTE:攻撃こそ最大の防御}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.01,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:825346,827014}We should focus on that.{NOTE:その意気込みでやらなくては}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.68,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:827014,828682}– Alright, Captain!\N– Roger that!{NOTE:—了解 キャプテン！\\N—了解！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.14,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:834313,836148}Let's hurry up and go to sleep.{NOTE:早く部屋に行って眠ることね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:57.85,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:836148,837858}Yeah, not a word.\NI'm gonna sleep like a log.{NOTE:言われなくてもバタンキューだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:13:59.94,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:838817,839943}Oh? Where's Ayuhara-san?{NOTE:あら？ 鮎原さんは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.19,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:840527,842196}She's stayed behind with Professor.{NOTE:まだ残ってます 先生と}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:08.03,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:845366,848035}I expected to see you here, Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原 やっぱり残っていたな}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:848035,849787}Please tell me, Professor!{NOTE:教えてください 先生}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:15.04,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:852039,855042}I gave my all\Nto obtain my current attack.{NOTE:先生 今のアタックでさえ 私には精いっぱいです}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:20.04,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:855042,860047}But what should I do if we need even more power?\NI just don't know what to do anymore.{NOTE:なのに これ以上の努力を 要求されるとしたら どうすればいいのか 見当もつきません}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.96,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:860047,861965}So you want me\Nto solve that problem for you.{NOTE:それを教えてほしいと言うのかね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:861965,863050}Yes sir.{NOTE:はい}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:25.46,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:863050,865469}You're asking too much, Ayuhara.{NOTE:ちょっと虫がよすぎるぞ 鮎原}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.47,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:865469,866470}Huh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:30.26,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:866470,870265}You can destroy this wall\Nthat's blocking you with your own power.{NOTE:自分の ぶつかった壁は 自分の力で たたき壊す他はない}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:33.01,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:870265,873018}But trying to overcome that wall\Nwith a ladder is not the way to go.{NOTE:人の力で壁に はしごを かけようとしても無駄だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:36.43,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:874853,876438}I can say only one thing.{NOTE:俺に言えることは 一つだけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:42.23,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:880359,882236}Get rid of your pride\Nas attack number one.{NOTE:アタックナンバーワンの 誇りを捨てろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:53.41,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:890953,893414}But I'm just thinking\Nabout our customers.{NOTE:でも お客さんの 利益を考えないようでは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:57.33,Default,Ichinose's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:893414,897334}That may be true, but if you keep doing this\Nwe might go out of business in this town!{NOTE:ああ しかし そんなことをしたら この街で商売が できなくなってしまうぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.50,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:897334,898502}That's nonsense!{NOTE:そんなバカな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.25,Default,Ichinose's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:898502,900254}Please don't yell, Tsutomu.{NOTE:それがしきたりなのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:03.88,Default,Ichinose's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:900254,903882}You'll inherit this shop either way.\NYou can do whatever you want with it.{NOTE:どうせ お前に譲る店だから お前の 好きなようにしていい}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:06.00,Default,Ichinose's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:903882,906009}But please, Tsutomu,\Neverything but that.{NOTE:でも努 それだけは やめてくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:06.92,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:906009,906927}Have it your way, Dad!{NOTE:分かったよ 父さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:09.47,Default,Ichinose's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:908554,909471}Tsutomu…{NOTE:努…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.30,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:910514,912307}Tsutomu-kun.{NOTE:努君}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.68,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:912307,913684}Oh… K-Kozue-kun?{NOTE:あっ… こずえ君}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:29.82,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:923527,929825}Whenever you try something new,\Na bump or two along the road should be expected.{NOTE:新しいことを しようとすれば そりゃあ 誰だって 一度や二度は 壁に ぶつかることもあるさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.45,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:929825,931452}Our business is no exception.{NOTE:僕の商売だってそうさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:37.49,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:931452,937499}If we buy directly from the production area, there's no place\Nfor the middleman, so we can sell our vegetables cheaply.{NOTE:産地から直接 野菜を 持ってきて売れば 中間業者が 入らなくなるから 野菜が安く売れる}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:41.42,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:937499,941420}But my dad says that's not possible\Nand just forbids me.{NOTE:この直売方式が 野菜に限っては できないんだよ こずえ君}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:42.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:941420,942296}Why?{NOTE:なぜ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.29,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:942296,944298}Because apparently no one\Nhas done it before.{NOTE:今まで やったとこがないからさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.59,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:944298,946592}If we were to try it,\Nwe'd get resistance from the other stores.{NOTE:やれば 他の店から抵抗がある}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.84,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:946592,948844}Dad's afraid of the backlash.{NOTE:おやじは それを心配して やるなって言うんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.30,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:948844,951305}But I still want to try it, Kozue-kun.{NOTE:しかし 僕は やってみたいんだ こずえ君}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:56.05,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:951305,956059}There never will be any progress unless we can\Novercome the boundaries set by common sense.{NOTE:常識を打ち破らなければ 何の進歩もないからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:956059,957394}You're right.{NOTE:そうね}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:00.77,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:957394,960772}In order to have progress,\Nwe must keep an open mind to possibilities.{NOTE:新しいものを 生み出すには 常識を打ち破らなくては いけないわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:962191,964902}I feel encouraged\Nafter hearing your words.{NOTE:私にも 何とか 自信が湧いてきたわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:07.52,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:964902,967529}Good. That's the spirit, Kozue-kun.{NOTE:うん そうだよ その意気だよ こずえ君}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:10.36,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:967529,970365}Do not hesitate. Go for it!{NOTE:何も迷うことはないんだ 頑張れよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.11,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:970365,972117}I will.{NOTE:私 やるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.70,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:972117,973702}Good luck, Kozue-kun.{NOTE:頑張れよ こずえ君}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:14.66,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:973702,974661}Thanks.{NOTE:ええ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.41,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:974661,977414}I'll go cheer you on\Nduring the prefectural qualifiers.{NOTE:県大会には必ず応援に行くよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.41,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:977414,978415}Thank you.{NOTE:ありがとう}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:35.22,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:991428,995224}Here's our strategy for the preliminaries.\NOonuma will give us a chance.{NOTE:県大会の作戦を言う大沼が チャンスボールを上げる}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:39.22,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:995224,999228}To accomplish that, we'll leave both reception\Nand toss completely up to Oonuma.{NOTE:そのため レシーブとトスの 完全一体化を 大沼には要求する}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.27,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:999228,1001271}Are you okay with that, Oonuma?{NOTE:分かるな？ 大沼}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.10,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001271,1002105}Yes sir!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:49.44,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004775,1009446}Then Hayakawa relays that toss with her long spike\Neither to the right or left end of the net.{NOTE:そのトスを 早川は ネットの右端か 左端へ ロングスパイクする}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.65,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009446,1010656}Yes sir.{NOTE:はい}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:55.07,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010656,1015077}The enemy will naturally think\Nthe ball will be an out.{NOTE:これは 敵の目をくらませ アウトと 思わせる以上 １センチの誤差も 許されない}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:58.87,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015077,1018872}Then at the last moment Ayuhara slams\NHayakawa's spike to the corner of the enemy's court.{NOTE:そして鮎原が 早川のスパイクを もう一度 敵のコーナーへ スパイクするんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:00.66,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018872,1020666}Just like I thought!{NOTE:や… やっぱり？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:04.87,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020666,1024878}Yes. Spiked balls are flying\Nat 30 to 40 km/h.{NOTE:そうだ スパイクボールは 時速30キロか 40キロで飛んでいる}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:11.34,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024878,1031343}You need to catch up with that ball,\Njump and spike rather than cutting it.{NOTE:そのボールに やや平行に 走りつつ ジャンプして スパイクボールを カットするように スパイクする}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.38,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031343,1033387}I named this technique\Na "double attack".{NOTE:これをダブルアタックと 名付けた}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033387,1034721}Double attack?{NOTE:ダブルアタック}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.61,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049736,1051613}Tenryū is pretty good.{NOTE:天竜ってすごいわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:32.82,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051613,1052823}They're a dark horse.{NOTE:ダークホースね}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:36.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052823,1056368}They have no distinct technique,\Nbut they have an outstanding team work.{NOTE:別に特徴はないけど 抜群のチームワークね}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.66,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056368,1058662}I think they might get\Nto the semifinals.{NOTE:決勝戦には 進出してくるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.53,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058662,1060539}So they'll play against…{NOTE:それに対するのは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:43.12,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060539,1063125}Either Misawa or us.{NOTE:美沢か 私たちのどちらかだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:46.08,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063125,1066086}Maybe we'll have to play with\NMisawa first, then Tenryū?{NOTE:第１難関が美沢で 第２が天竜か}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:48.33,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066086,1068338}We should be thinking about\Nhow to play against Tenryū, too.{NOTE:天竜対策も考えて おかなければね}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:49.63,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068338,1069631}Kozue?{NOTE:こずえ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.00,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069631,1071008}Kozue!{NOTE:こずえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071008,1072259}Ah, huh?{NOTE:あっ… えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.92,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072259,1073927}Kozue. What are you doing?{NOTE:こずえ 何してんの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:55.80,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073927,1075804}People are talking to you, you know.{NOTE:人が大事な話を してるときに}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.30,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075804,1077306}I'm sorry.{NOTE:ごめんなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077306,1080183}It's just I can't see\NTsutomu-kun anywhere.{NOTE:さっきから努君 捜してるんだけど 来てないのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.10,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080183,1082102}Don't worry, he must be busy.{NOTE:いいじゃない 忙しいのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082102,1083937}Midori…{NOTE:みどり}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:09.23,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085355,1089234}Alright, girls, prepare yourselves.\NWe're playing against Matsubara High next.{NOTE:さあ みんな 準備しろ 相手は松原高校だぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:11.02,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1089234,1091028}– Yes sir.\N– Yes sir.{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.65,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1091028,1092654}– Kozue.\N– Y-Yeah.{NOTE:—こずえ \\N—う うん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:25.62,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104249,1105626}He's still not here…{NOTE:まだ来てないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.17,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105626,1108170}Maybe something's wrong?\NMaybe something happen—{NOTE:どうかしたのかしら何かあったのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.33,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108170,1110339}Kozue, chance ball!{NOTE:こずえ チャンスボール！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.68,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121183,1122684}What are you doing?{NOTE:何やってんのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.06,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122684,1124061}What are you doing…?{NOTE:何やってんのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.18,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124061,1125187}What are you doing!?{NOTE:何やってんのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.64,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125187,1126647}Do not hesitate, Ayuhara!{NOTE:迷うな 鮎原}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.27,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131068,1132277}{\an8}Ah, what a close call.{NOTE:危ない 危ない}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.73,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132277,1134738}{\an8}Who'd think Matsubara would give us problems.{NOTE:松原に こんなに てこずるなんてさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.90,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133528,1135906}Kozue, come here for a bit.{NOTE:こずえ ちょっとちょっと}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.61,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135906,1137616}What was with you today?{NOTE:一体 どうしたっていうの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:02.24,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137616,1142245}We might've won,\Nbut you've played like a novice!{NOTE:今日は運よく勝てたから いいようなものの あなた 凡ミスの 連続じゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:04.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142245,1144373}I'm sorry.{NOTE:ご… ごめんなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:07.37,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144373,1147376}Tomorrow we're playing against Numazu.\NGet a grip!{NOTE:明日は沼津と対戦なのよ しっかりしてよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:09.16,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147334,1149169}Hayakawa-san, that's enough.{NOTE:早川さん もういいわよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.58,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149169,1150587}But Captain!{NOTE:でも キャプテン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.17,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150587,1152172}Good luck tomorrow, Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:明日は 頑張ってね 鮎原さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152172,1153799}Sure.{NOTE:はい}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:16.51,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153799,1156510}I'm sure Tsutomu-san\Nwill come see you tomorrow.{NOTE:あしたは来てくれるわよ 努さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:17.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156510,1157761}Yeah…{NOTE:ええ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:23.68,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160514,1163684}It's the greengrocer man!\NCheap fruits! Very cheap!{NOTE:八百屋です 安いよ とっても安いよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:27.10,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163684,1167104}Fresh fruits, very cheap!{NOTE:新鮮なお野菜がとっても安いんです 八百屋ですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:29.73,Default,Housewife,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167104,1169731}Oh, Toko-chan?\NIs what they're offering really that special?{NOTE:トコちゃん どっかの 八百屋さんで特売やってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:33.73,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169731,1173735}It is! You can get a radish for 80 yen.\NSecond one will be for half price!{NOTE:ええ そうよ 大根１本 80円 ２本買うと120円よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:35.52,Default,Housewife,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173735,1175529}Aren't you just playing house?{NOTE:おままごとの 八百屋さんでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:39.86,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175529,1179866}Nope! The store is real!\NHurry up or it's all gonna sold out!{NOTE:違うの お兄ちゃんのお店よ早く行かないと 売り切れちゃいますよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.74,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1179866,1180742}Oh dear.{NOTE:まあ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.03,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180742,1182035}Welcome, welcome!{NOTE:さあ いらっしゃい いらっしゃい}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:44.87,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182035,1184871}Ichinose's mobile supermarket!\NWe got great discounts!{NOTE:一ノ瀬青果の直売方式による 移動販売です}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.83,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184871,1186832}Welcome, welcome!\NVery cheap prices!{NOTE:さあ 安いですよ 安いですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:48.58,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186832,1188583}Welcome, welcome!{NOTE:さあ いらっしゃい いらっしゃい}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.46,Default,Housewife,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188583,1190460}– I'd like these. – Yes ma'am.\N– And this one.{NOTE:ねえ これ頂戴 これも もらうわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:54.46,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190460,1194464}Sure thing. Let's see…\NThat'll be 350 yen total.{NOTE:あっ どうも はい えっと 全部で350円ですね}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:55.75,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1194464,1195757}– Here.\N– Thank you.{NOTE:—はい\\N—ありがとうございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:58.05,Default,Housewife,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195757,1198051}Hey, pretty eyes.\NDo you have some potatoes?{NOTE:ねえ 八百屋さん じゃがいも頂戴}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.14,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200762,1203140}Well, that'll be 150 yen.{NOTE:えっと はい 150円 頂きます}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:04.93,Default,Housewife,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203140,1204933}Wow, it really is cheap.{NOTE:まあ ほんとに安いのね}
