Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:33.00,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231835,1233003}Oh.{NOTE:まあ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.42,Default,Housewife,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233003,1235422}How can you be making a profit\Nwith such prices?{NOTE:あんた これじゃ もうけがないでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:41.01,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235422,1241011}Oh, I can sell them fresh and so cheap\Nbecause I contracted the producers directly.{NOTE:いいえ 産地の生産者と契約して 直接運んでくるから 新鮮な野菜を安く売れるんですよ}
