Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:07.28,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264451,1267287}Sorry I didn't come\Nto cheer for you today, Kozue-kun.{NOTE:こずえ君 今日は 応援を すっぽかしてごめんね}
