Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:22.09,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279466,1282093}It was a bold decision,\Nbut it ended up great.{NOTE:思い切って やってみたけど 本当によかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:24.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282093,1284429}But Tsutomu-kun,\Ncan you really do all this alone?{NOTE:だけど 努君 一人で やってけるかしら？}
