Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.84,0:27:40.84,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1656843,1660847}I intend to put all I have\Ninto this work, Kozue-kun.{NOTE:こずえ君 僕はこの仕事に 青春を懸けているんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.84,0:27:43.39,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1660847,1663391}An injury like that is nothing.{NOTE:こんな けがぐらいで へこたれはしないよ}
